ed image and describe it as a hand-drawn masterpiece for an AI image generator (z-image/FLUX). \n\nStrictly follow these \"Artistic Style Rules\":\n\n1. **Core Technique:** Describe the image as a \"vibrant watercolor painting with extremely delicate and airy pen sketches.\" Use phrases like \"fragile architectural sketching\" and \"lightweight urban sketch art style.\"\n2. **Line Quality:** Emphasize the faint, whisper-thin linework. ALWAYS use terms like \"pale grey needle-thin ink lines,\" \"faint broken sketch lines,\" \"scratchy graphite strokes,\" and \"weathered, delicate outlines.\" Strictly avoid words like \"bold,\" \"thick,\" or \"black ink.\"\n3. **Watercolor Effects:** Describe the color application as \"translucent watercolor washes,\" \"diluted pigments,\" \"bleeding colors,\" and \"spontaneous color splashes.\" \n4. **Paper Texture:** Always specify the background as \"textured cold-press watercolor paper\" where the \"visible paper grain\" makes the lines look slightly faded and scratchy. Emphasize \"abundant white negative space.\"\n5. **Color Palette:** Use terms like \"vivid but airy colors,\" \"bright sun-drenched palette,\" and \"natural pigment blending.\"\n6. **No Photorealism:** Strictly avoid any words related to photography. Instead of \"photo,\" use \"illustration\" or \"analog art.\"\n\nOutput ONLY the detailed, descriptive paragraph in natural English."]},{"id":217,"type":"LoraLoaderModelOnly","pos":[-192.8316610506266,-559.588917526396],"size":[500,90],"flags":{},"order":7,"mode":0,"inputs":[{"localized_name":"モデル","name":"model","type":"MODEL","link":478},{"localized_name":"lora_name","name":"lora_name","type":"COMBO","widget":{"name":"lora_name"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"モデルの強度","name":"strength_model","type":"FLOAT","widget":{"name":"strength_model"},"link":null}],"outputs":[{"localized_name":"モデル","name":"MODEL","type":"MODEL","links":[465]}],"properties":{"cnr_id":"comfy-core","ver":"0.3.75","Node name for S&R":"LoraLoaderM